My Current Play List

KennyHoopla

How Will I Rest in Peace if I'm Buried by a Highway?

If you do nothing else after browsing this list, go out and listen to this brilliant album.

Royal & the Serpent

Overwhelmed

This song is the voice of anyone who has ever suffered from anxiety.

They Might be Giants

Flood

One of the few albums I can sing cover to cover, Flood could easily be the soundtrack of my life.

Twenty One Pilots

Jumpsuit

It's not the only Twenty One Pilots song in my playlist, but it probably gets the heaviest rotation.

Alien Ant Farm

Smooth Criminal

Annie, are you okay? Are you okay, Annie?

Arjana

R.E.M.

I don't care if it's trite; this was 2020's theme song.

Violent Femmes

Cake
